    <item>
      <title>Setting up a Static Website.</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/post-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 12:00:00 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/post-1/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;My experience of hosting a static website Hugo on Github Pages with the Hextra theme.
All the documentation was stellar and I will also link below if you need further instructions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;How do you even begin?&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;It wasn&amp;rsquo;t too bad in my opinion! I was able to use &lt;a
    href=&#34;https://docs.github.com/en/pages&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Github Pages&lt;/a&gt; for mine.\&lt;/p&gt;
